# PS Sandbox Plan-Only Testing

For migration web app validation in this repo:

- Use the `PS Sandbox` project only when selecting a project in the application.
- Treat browser and workflow validation as plan-only unless the user explicitly authorizes destructive actions with the required approval token.
- Do not run deploy/apply or destroy while validating profile rollout work unless the user explicitly changes this instruction.
- If existing app state points at a different project, switch back to `PS Sandbox` before continuing.
